  "synopsis": "Domo-kun and Charo meet a strange girl in the hustle and bustle Tokyo. Since \"that day\", she has not gone back home. When Charo gives the girl a wreath of Gerbera plants, she accidentally sneezes. A burst of magic came out of the Gerbera, and a flower train emerges from the middle of a flower garden. As the three board the flower train, it starts moving toward the girl's hometown. However, what awaits them is a ferocious storm!\n\nAnimated short to support the reconstruction of areas hit by the 2011 Great Eastern Japan Earthquake.\n\n(Source: Official website)",
